[I] Production quality, multilayer virtual switch

[T] Open vSwitch is a production quality, multilayer virtual switch. It is
[T] designed to enable massive network automation through programmatic
[T] extension, while still supporting standard management interfaces and
[T] protocols (e.g. NetFlow, sFlow, IPFIX, RSPAN, CLI, LACP, 802.1ag).

[U] https://www.openvswitch.org/

